data.description: This quaint starter home features two bedrooms and a charming back patio, offering a perfect balance of comfort and simplicity. Conveniently located minutes from the freeway, it provides easy access to local stores and restaurants. Ideal for those seeking a cozy, low-maintenance living space close to everyday amenities. Ask your realtor about getting into this home with the new MFA program covering the entire downpayment!
